## Proposed Changes

### Project Initialization

#### [NEW] Next.js 14 App Router project at `d:\portfolio`

- `npx -y create-next-app@latest ./ --ts --tailwind --eslint --app --src-dir --import-alias "@/*"` (non-interactive)
- Install: `framer-motion`, `@next/third-parties`, `react-intersection-observer`

---

