- **Videos tab**: Horizontal scroll carousel of 9:16 thumbnails, click opens modal with video playback

#### [NEW] [GalleryModal.tsx](file:///d:/portfolio/src/components/GalleryModal.tsx)
- Fullscreen overlay, swipe/arrow navigation for artwork images

#### [NEW] [VideoModal.tsx](file:///d:/portfolio/src/components/VideoModal.tsx)
- Modal with 9:16 video player

#### [NEW] [galleryData.ts](file:///d:/portfolio/src/data/galleryData.ts)
- Artwork array `{ id, title, category, images[] }` + Video array `{ id, src, thumbnail }`

