## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests

- `npm run build` — Ensure production build completes without errors
- `npm run lint` — No ESLint warnings

### Browser Verification

1. Start dev server with `npm run dev`
2. Open `http://localhost:3000` in browser
3. Verify each section renders correctly:
   - Hero: profile image carousel cycles every 2s
   - About: video placeholder visible, text animation triggers on scroll
   - Gallery: masonry grid displays, filters work, modal opens with slider
   - Video Gallery: horizontal scroll works, modal opens
   - Contact: form fields have focus animations, social icons have glow
4. Verify responsive design at mobile (375px), tablet (768px), desktop (1440px)
5. Verify custom cursor works on desktop and hides on mobile
6. Check particle background renders without performance issues

### Manual Verification

- Ask user to review the website in the browser and confirm it meets their aesthetic expectations
